title: UFYB 117: Result-Entitlement
itunes:title: Result-Entitlement
description:
Listen in as I take a deep dive into entitlement, how it shows up and why, and a new way to start thinking about the results you want that will save you time and energy, instead of sitting in entitlement, which drains all of your resources and leaves you in emotional drama.

Get full show notes and more information here: http://unfuckyourbrain.com/117
